<div class="tag">
<a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e8%af%97%e7%bb%8f">诗经</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e5%86%99%e9%b8%9f">写鸟</a>
<span>，</span><a href="https://www.gushiwen.org/shiwen/default.aspx?tstr=%e6%8a%92%e6%83%85">抒情</a>
</div>
